name: Rome Fortune - Lemon Squeeze feat YEO Cig prod. Snakehips

metadata.name: Rome Fortune - Lemon Squeeze feat YEO Cig (prod. Snakehips)
metadata.description:
Atlanta emcee Rome Fortune has teamed up with Bronx street legend and fellow rapper YEO Cig for his latest single ‘Lemon Squeeze’, produced by UK duo Snakehips.

Off the back of writing the latest Channel Tres and Yung Bae certified hit single ‘Wonder’, Rome returns with the sunkissed ‘Lemon Squeeze’, a welcome return for the artist as his distinctive drawl layers the future funk and disco beats of Snakehips.

NFT Experience for Holders: 
All proceeds of the NFT will go to the RomeyHomies treasury focused on building an Artist Incubator in Atlanta. 

If you are a holder learn more at romeyshomies.com
